 Jennifer, a 200 level student of Niger Delta University (NDU), in Bayelsa State, was on Sunday, June 11, reportedly found dead in her apartment with multiple stab injuries and bullet wounds. According to reports, the deceased was killed after a fierce struggle with her killer, who also cut off her finger, before leaving her in the pool of her own blood. She was said to have been shot in the back and was found dead days after she was killed, as her body was already decomposing when she was found. The reports also claimed that police operatives confirmed that the bullets found on her were not local bullets. It was gathered that a close friend of the deceased disclosed that her boyfriend, Jay, has been abusing her over allegations of cheating. Jay was also said to have used her phone to confessed to the crime and threatened to commit suicide in her department’s WhatsApp group. Below are chats allegedly shared on Jennifer’s department WhatsApp group by her boyfriend: <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-10653 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/twxHurY.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i1.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-14-at-7.40.16-AM.jpeg?resize=440,545&amp;ssl=1" alt="How Solider allegedly rapes, kills girlfriend and cut off her finger over cheating" width="440" height="545" data-recalc-dims="1"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-10653 lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i0.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/twxHurY.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i1.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/WhatsApp-Image-2021-07-14-at-7.40.16-AM.jpeg?resize=440%2C545&#038;ssl=1" alt="How Solider allegedly rapes, kills girlfriend and cut off her finger over cheating" width="440" height="545" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/twxHurY.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https: